Over 140 years in business. 👏🏾⁠
⁠
Meet E.E. Ward Moving & Storage — the oldest Black-owned business in America, founded in 1881. From helping enslaved people escape to freedom via the Underground Railroad to becoming a leader in logistics today, this company’s story is nothing short of legendary. 📦⁠
⁠
Tap the link in bio to learn how they’ve built a legacy that still thrives today. #BlackExcellence⁠
